nodes.text: Tesser was an X'Ting who lived before the Clone Wars. He was the broodmate and brother of Jesson Di Blinth, a member of the X'Ting Hive Council. He died in a cave while searching for the Royal X'Ting eggs. Jesson and Obi-Wan Kenobi found his body tied to a rock, presumably so that he would not fall to the carnivorous worms that inhabited the caves if he passed out.
